<li><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/recipes/recipe_page.php?article=81&rsa=Make%20Poison&sb=item&sub=dye&menustr=080080020000">Dye Recipes made with Mortar & Pestle</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/recipes/recipe_page.php?article=52&rsa=Make%20Poison&sb=item&sub=chargedpotion&menustr=080080030000">Multiple Dose Poison Recipes</a></li>
